
This directory contains software components that are split up in so-called
packages. The following list describes the core packages and those that are
not self descriptive:

Core packages:

- bootstrap                      L4 system boot loader / Boot-image generator
- io/io                          Io server, maintains the platform
                                 and I/O resources
- io/libio                       Interface and library to access device
                                 resources (e.g. MMIO, IRQs)
- io/libio-io                    Specific interface library code for
                                 the io server.
- io/libio-direct                Direct io interface.
- io/libvbus                     Virtual bus library for devices
- l4re-core/crtn                 Program startup support, part of C environment
- l4re-core/cxx                  Small low-level C++ library containing, for
                                 example, data structures such as AVL trees,
                                 lists, bitmaps, and an L4 IPC framework
- l4re-core/cxx_libc_io          Basic low-level stream back-end
- l4re-core/l4re                 L4 Runtime Environment interfaces and library,
                                 C++ version
- l4re-core/l4re_c               C interface for L4 Runtime Environment
- l4re-core/l4re_kernel          L4Re process manager
- l4re-core/l4re_vfs             L4Re Virtual Filesystem infrastructure
- l4re-core/l4sys                Kernel bindings
- l4re-core/l4util               Utility functions
- l4re-core/ldscripts            Linker scripts
- l4re-core/ldso                 Dynamic library support
- l4re-core/libc_backends        Glue code between C library and
                                 L4 Runtime Environment
                                 such as memory and file handling
- l4re-core/libgcc               GCC runtime support, L4 variant
- l4re-core/libgcc-pure          GCC runtime support, bare-metal variant
- l4re-core/libkproxy            Support for kernel interface proxies
- l4re-core/libloader            Support library for l4re and moe.
- l4re-core/libsigma0            Sigma0 API library.
- l4re-core/libstdc++-headers    Standard C++ library headers
- l4re-core/libstdc++-v3         Standard C++ library, multi-threaded variant.
- l4re-core/libstdc++-v3-minimal Standard C++ library, single-threaded
                                 variant.
- l4re-core/libsupc++            Standard C++ Runtime Environment,
                                 multi-threaded variant.
- l4re-core/libsupc++-minimal    Standard C++ Runtime Environment,
                                 single-threaded variant.
- l4re-core/lua                  Lua interpreter and library
- l4re-core/moe                  L4 Root task (essential L4 program)
- l4re-core/ned                  Scriptable application launcher
- l4re-core/sigma0               L4 Root pager (essential L4 program)
- l4re-core/ucblic               Standard C library, including POSIX
                                 thread environment
- l4re-core/ucblic-minimal       Single-threaded variant of the C library

Other packages:

- ankh                        Network server and switch
- boost-lite                  Subset of the boost library
- cons                        Console multiplexer
- dope                        DOpE windowing system
- drivers                     Driver libraries
- drivers-frst                Driver libraries
- examples                    Examples
- fb-drv                      Framebuffer driver server
- hello                       'Hello World!' example
- input                       Driver library for input devices
                              (PS2: Keyboard, Mouse)
- l4con                       Graphical console
- l4virtio                    VirtIO interfaces, including L4-based
                              transports
- libc_be_stdin               Simple libc backend for stdin
- libevent                    Library for event handling
- libfdt                      Flattened device tree library
- libgomp                     Open MP library for gcc
- libirq                      Convenience library for IRQ handling.
- libpng                      libpng graphics library.
- libsdl*                     SDL library
- libvcpu                     Support for handling vCPUs
- loader                      L4Re program loader
- log                         Library for debug logging support
- lxfuxlibc                   Support library for Fiasco-UX specific programs
- mag                         Windowing system
- mag-gfx                     Graphic routines
- rtc                         Real-Time clock service
- scout*                      Text browser
- shmc                        Communication infracture based on shared memory
- uvmm                        Virtual machine monitor
- virtio-net                  VirtIO-based virtual network switch
- zlib                        zlib compression library
